              <div class="slide-content" id="slide-1-content">
                <h2>Distributed programming</h2>
                <p>
                  No more writing encoders and decoders at every network
                  boundary.
                  <strong
                    >Say where you want computations to run and it
                    happens</strong
                  >
                  ðŸ”® â€” Dependencies are deployed on the fly.
                </p>

                <a
                  href="/docs/the-big-idea/"
